    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >目前版本已支持手柄与改键！并推出了简单模式！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/d353272a13d8737ff62c3b6b00aedce1.avif?t=1649728645\" width=600 height=113 /></span><br>设想一下，如果你是一位美丽的公主，却被一只想要除掉你未婚夫的怪物绑架到深渊会怎样？ <br>这就是她的遭遇。15岁的她本可以寻求未婚夫的帮助，但为了证明自己的实力，毅然决然独自踏上逃出深渊的漫漫旅途。<br>探索各个关卡，击败不断出现的敌人。<br>夺位的新王，深渊之王身陷囹圄！<br>深渊暗流涌动，是谁封印了旧王？<br>究竟发生了什么？ <br>探寻真相，找到回家之路。<br>她能独自逃出深渊吗？<br>她的未婚夫究竟是何人？<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/2e125d77b2066d27f57d1486e9381ffc.avif?t=1649728645\" width=600 height=113 /></span><br>● 硬核的横版跳跃动作，它可能一点都不比蔚蓝简单<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/60109b3c16c303bc24d7e3aa9a9aad23.avif?t=1649728645\" width=600 height=113 /></span><br>● 全新的攻击系统，可同时使用冲刺与攻击<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/69d463a4003b17a34f5cfcc5acffdd6d.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/69d463a4003b17a34f5cfcc5acffdd6d.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/69d463a4003b17a34f5cfcc5acffdd6d.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 冲刺时会短暂进入无敌状态，可用于躲避陷阱或敌人的攻击<br><br>● 像素风格横版战斗搭配现代视觉特效 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/4a0e03171a60a3b885765714c45fd17c.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/4a0e03171a60a3b885765714c45fd17c.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/4a0e03171a60a3b885765714c45fd17c.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 流畅的2D操作。灵活运用冲刺，奔跑，跳跃和斩击来对付各种强敌。 <br><br>● 探索熔岩之地、绿荫之地、陷阱之地、炸弹之地、暗影之地等风格迥异的区域。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/902d3304746e7cf0c1bf036ad6435633.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/902d3304746e7cf0c1bf036ad6435633.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/902d3304746e7cf0c1bf036ad6435633.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/0f275586e0970ad1aa60ee28d585a074.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/0f275586e0970ad1aa60ee28d585a074.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/0f275586e0970ad1aa60ee28d585a074.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/1207f0edffded0c504ccd87b5a9628d4.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/1207f0edffded0c504ccd87b5a9628d4.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/1207f0edffded0c504ccd87b5a9628d4.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/50e29b9b01325f6ba9bc69751fd3481e.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/50e29b9b01325f6ba9bc69751fd3481e.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/50e29b9b01325f6ba9bc69751fd3481e.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 通过暴食之力获得强大的新技能！血斩、雷击和百裂斩！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/e3a48aa334f6b70cda6e3404adb3db31.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/e3a48aa334f6b70cda6e3404adb3db31.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/e3a48aa334f6b70cda6e3404adb3db31.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 种类繁多的敌人和头目<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/2bdf680f060b5cc9a500591ddb2a17b9.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/2bdf680f060b5cc9a500591ddb2a17b9.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/2bdf680f060b5cc9a500591ddb2a17b9.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 各种致命的陷阱！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/326bd6d0104cb23d1dd6f68b2b911a5d.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/326bd6d0104cb23d1dd6f68b2b911a5d.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/326bd6d0104cb23d1dd6f68b2b911a5d.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/878a8f55fe59094fa2df12fa5802725e.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/878a8f55fe59094fa2df12fa5802725e.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/878a8f55fe59094fa2df12fa5802725e.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/a35dc6e4b9bdb52939fafbd7fc158410.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/a35dc6e4b9bdb52939fafbd7fc158410.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/a35dc6e4b9bdb52939fafbd7fc158410.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/7e93c035acccecd53135977c0748dd6e.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/7e93c035acccecd53135977c0748dd6e.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/7e93c035acccecd53135977c0748dd6e.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 还有许多可收集的道具，例如：<br>飞翔草莓：恢复生命值。<br>羽翼：深渊中的货币。<br>独特果实：恢复暴食之力。<br>暴食之星：赋予你新的技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/aefa27e2529bc665ce86ca9953aa45bb.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/aefa27e2529bc665ce86ca9953aa45bb.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/aefa27e2529bc665ce86ca9953aa45bb.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
